nodes.text: In 19 BBY, a cantina in Coruscant's lower levels was where police officers with the Coruscant Security Force chased a thief into and cornered him there. The believed he was a Jedi as the thief had cut off the hand of an officer with a lightsaber and they called for backup. Squad 40 from the 501st Legion arrived and stormed the cantina, killing the thief.
